# Ignore Numlock and other modifiers for bindings
IgnoreModifiers L25

# Applications
Silent Key Return A 4 Exec $[TERMINAL]
Silent Key b A 4 Exec chromium
Silent Key b A 4s Exec chromium --incognito
Silent Key d A 4 Exec dmenurun
Silent Key q A 4 Exec qute
Silent Key e A 4 Exec dmenuunicode
Silent Key e A 4s Exec dmenukaomoji
Silent Key w A 4s Exec wpa-cute
Silent Key v A 4 Exec $[TERMINAL] -e vim
Silent Key f A 4 Exec $[TERMINAL] -e ranger
Silent Key m A 4s Exec dmenumount
Silent Key u A 4s Exec dmenuunmount
Silent Key plus A 4 Exec xzoom
Silent Key F8 A 4 Exec recorder
Silent Key Print A N Exec flameshot gui
Silent Key F1 A N Exec /dev/null

# Audio Control
Silent Key XF86AudioLowerVolume A N Exec pactl set-sink-volume 0 -1%
Silent Key XF86AudioRaiseVolume A N Exec pactl set-sink-volume 0 +1%
Silent Key XF86AudioMute A N Exec pactl set-sink-mute 0 toggle

# Backlight Control
Silent Key XF86MonBrightnessDown A N Exec xbacklight -dec 1
Silent Key XF86MonBrightnessUp A N Exec xbacklight -inc 1

# System
Silent Key r A 4s Exec rebooting
Silent Key q A 4s Exec shuttingdown
Silent Key r A 4 Restart

# Windows Control
Silent Key F11 WT 4s Thumbnail
Silent Key F11 WT 4 Maximize 100 100
Silent Key Up WT 4 Maximize 100 100
Silent Key Down WT 4 Thumbnail
Silent Key c WT 4s Close
Silent Key Tab A M SwitchWindow
Silent Key h WT 4 TileLeft
Silent Key j WT 4 TileBottom
Silent Key k WT 4 TileTop
Silent Key l WT 4 TileRight
Silent Key u WT 4 Resize w-1 keep
Silent Key i WT 4 Resize keep w-1
Silent Key o WT 4 Resize keep w+1
Silent Key p WT 4 Resize w+1 keep
Silent Key h WT 4s Move w-1 keep
Silent Key j WT 4s Move keep w+1
Silent Key k WT 4s Move keep w-1
Silent Key l WT 4s Move w+1 keep

